org.springframework.kafka.core

类 DefaultKafkaConsumerFactory<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.kafka.core.DefaultKafkaConsumerFactory<K,V>
  • 类型参数:
    K - the key type.
    V - the value type.
    所有已实现的接口:
    ConsumerFactory<K,V>

    public class DefaultKafkaConsumerFactory<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ConsumerFactory<K,V>
    The ConsumerFactory implementation to produce a new Consumer instance for provided Map configs and optional Deserializer keyDeserializer, valueDeserializer implementations on each createConsumer() invocation.

If a factory does not implement this method, ConsumerFactory.createConsumer(String, String) is invoked, ignoring the prefix. TODO: remove default in 2.2
